Our Online library lets you borrow your favorite books.To borrow a book customers 
must subscribe to our library subsription plan first.Customers can browes books 
through the library websites or through borrow now links on other websites.Fines 
and subscription fees are paid online.

The program has many objectives, according to CEO, including the ability to lend books
online,so consumers don't have to visit the physical store to borrow books, handling 
online request form the backend, and alleviating the need for physical visists.

The online lending system will make it easier for consumer to borrow books from libraries,
and receive them at home.

Upon reading the books, the customer is simply required to return them by  mail within a month
of borrowing them or else a fine of 2-5 BD may apply, ohterwise it depends on the circumstances.
